quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  13,35,"Akarorero k’Ijuru bemerewe kubatinya Imana yabo y’ukuri, imbere yabo niho haca imyonga n’ivyamwa vyaho nivy’ubuzima budahera hamwe n’igitutu caho nyene, aya niyo maherezo ya bamwe bemera Imana yabo yukuri, n’imperuka y’abahakanyi b’Imana nimuriro udahera gusa"
  13,36,"Nabo twahaye igitabu banezerezwa nivyo wamanuriwe nomumirwi yabo bahakanyi b’Imana harimwo ivyo banka, bimwe muri ibi, rero nuvuge uti:- jewe nategetswe gusenga Imana yanje gusa, kandi sindayigereranya n’ibindi bintu, niyo ntakambira kandi niwe niho hari ingaruka yanje"
  13,37,"Uku rero niko twamanuye iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu mugihe ari itegeko ry’Imana ryamanuwe muririmi rw’icarabu, niwakurikira itamariro ryabo mugihe umaze gushikirwa nubu bumenyi umenye yuko utazoba ukironse umugenzi canke uwugukingira imbere y’Imana"
  13,38,"Twararungitse intumwa z’Imana imbere yawe, nukubaha abakenyezi hamwe n’ibibondo, kandi ntibishoboka kuntumwa y’Imana kuzana igitangaro icarico cose atari kw’itegeko ry’Imana, rero umwanya uwariwo wose urafise amategeko yanditwse n’Imana"
  13,39,"Imana ihanagura ivyo yishakiye n’ukuvyemeza, kandi n’amamuko y’amategeko yose ari ku Mana yonyene"
  13,40,"Tukweretse bimwe mubihano twabemereye canke tukwishe, rero kuri wewe gushikana ubutumwa bwivyo wategetswe kugira gusa, no hejuru yacu nukuba harura gusa k’umusi w’imperuka"
  13,41,"Mbega ntibabonye yuko dushikira Isi yabo nukuyi gabangura kumbibe zayo, n’Imana itegeka k’ukuri, kandi ntawuharira kw’itegeko ryayo, nayo iroroshe muguharura"
  13,42,"Baragize ingeso bamwe batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri bamwe bamyeho imbere yabo, mugabo ingeso zose niku Mana kuko niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo ikiremwa muntu wese agira nayo abahakanyi b’Imana yabo y’ukuri bazotahura inyishu nziza y’ingoro yo mw’Ijuru yuko izoba ari ayande"